The NEWS file for the rivendell-install package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.7.2 --  11/18/2016

   Fourth BETA release.

   Updated RHEL 7 instructions to use nmtui(8) rather than nmcli(8) for
   the initial network configuration.

   Added several packages to the base RHEL7 installation. See the ChangeLog
   for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.7.1 --  7/19/2016

   Third BETA release.

   Added '--server' and '--client' installation modes for both RHEL-6
   and RHEL-7.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.6.1 --  6/30/2016

   Second BETA release.

   Added a 'install_rivendell_devel' script for installing the development
   environment for Rivendell to an existing RHEL Rivendell setup.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.6.0 --  6/28/2016

   Initial BETA release.  Support for RHEL 7 only.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
